  m_text: "Here survivors prepare for their next scavenge run. \nGear in better condition
    = survivor has higher chance of return with better and more plentiful loot.\nGear
    in bad condition = survivor has lower chance of return. If he does return the
    loot is worse and in lesser quantity."
