  m_text: "\tSurvivors are reporting that it's getting diffcult to find antibiotics.
    Soon they won't be able to find anymore antibiotics in this sector.\n\n\tKill
    all zombies left in this sector before your survivors can move to the next one.\n\n\tHopefully,
    they will find more antibiotics there before the infection gets you."
